marketing-text: Isikhulumi somthombo ovulekile wedatha ye-COVID19. Ideshibhodi ethuthukisiwe enwetshwe yisiphequluli ne-REST API yamahhala enemininingwane, eyenziwe yasendaweni kuzo zonke izilimi.
name: Igama
promo-message: Kwenziwe uthando ❤️ yiqembu ku-Hoobu.com. Hlela uhambo lwakho lwangemva kobhubhane manje nge-plan yethu yangempela yokubambisana esisebenzayo
general-advice-wash-hands-description: Geza izandla zakho njalo imizuzwana engama-20 usebenzisa insipho namanzi ngemuva kokuthi ushaye ikhala, ukukhwehlela noma ukuthunga ngaphambi kokudla noma ukuphatha ukudla. Ukugeza izandla ngendlela eyiyo kuyindlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokubulala amagciwane.
general-advice-minimise-contact-descript: Nciphisa emihlanganweni engabalulekile & uhambo futhi ufune ezinye izindlela zokubingelela njengokuxhawula izandla, ukubingelela noma ukwanga.
general-advice-avoid-face-description: Izandla zingathatha kalula amagciwane futhi uma zingcolile, izandla zingadlulisela leli gciwane emehlweni akho, ekhaleni noma emlonyeni. Ukusuka lapho, leli gciwane lingangena emzimbeni wakho likwenze ugule.
general-advice-be-hygienic-description: Ukumboza umlomo nekhala ngommese noma ngethambo lakho eligobile lapho ukhohlela noma uthimula, bese ulahla izicubu ezisetshenzisiwe ngokushesha.
general-advice-self-isolate-description: Uma uthola umkhuhlane onjengezimpawu kufanele uhlukane nakho njengendlela yokuvikela futhi uvikele ubungozi bokusabalalisa ukutheleleka ngokuhlala ekhaya.
